<p>
This is a series of posters commemorating various graphical user 
interface elements and applications which did not stand the test of time.
</p><p>
If you have any ideas for things to put in next posters,
<a href='contact'>let me know</a>! The posters are originally designed for
27&rdquo;&times;41&rdquo; (one-sheet) format, but can be scaled down even to A4
while still looking good.
</p>

<br>

